```

### As Status Indicators

Use appropriate badge colors to indicate status:

```html
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);">
    <span class="body-text">Order Status:</span>
    <span class="badge badge-success">
        <span class="badge-text">Shipped</span>
    </span>
</div>
```

### In Form Labels

Badges can be used with form labels to indicate required fields or field status:

```html
<div class="text-input size-medium">
    <div class="label">
        <span class="label-text">Username</span>
        <span class="badge badge-inline">
            <span class="badge-text">Required</span>
        </span>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Enter username">
    </div>
</div>
```

By following these guidelines, you'll create consistent, effective badges that align with the design system's principles and enhance the user experience.
